phrases: Kageyama Shigeo, also known as Mob.
The second year of middle school kicks off the most sensitive period in one's life.
Some hone their bodies playing sports,
some work hard on their studies,
some devote themselves to their hobbies,
and some fall for the opposite sex
and get a taste of bittersweet love.
All those youthful desires come together to form the amalgamation that is adolescence.
And Mob was spending that precious time working as
an assistant at a psychic business for 300 yen an hour.
The curse that is on your shoulder is

I will lift the curse now.
I am not paying for this.
where he relieves the stress from physical fatigue
and gets ride of stiff shoulders and back pain.

but do your shoulders still feel heavy?
I am sorry that I doubted you.

So the 40-minute massage course fee comes to 3,800 yen.
Do not call it the massage fee!
You will eat some will not you, Mob?
Master Reigen, you are getting much better at massages.
I have been trying various methods to improve,
like reading books on Seitai and stuff.
If there are 3 evil spirits, the exorcism fee on 1 of them will be on the house!!
Of course, it is only effective because of spiritual power.
You never try to start a conversation.
Well, I can use a little ESP and I am different from other people,
so I came to discuss that with you and ended up becoming your student.
At the time, I did not have anyone else to talk to, so I am grateful,
because you teach me various things and pay me.
That is what I have been thinking lately.
Does he think his pay is too little?
Or did he finally find me out?
Rather than things ending with me working part-time after school,
I have a feeling that there may or may not be
some other things that I can only experience now...
Is there something that you want to do right now?
No, I do not have anything particular in mind.
There is no need to rush into things.
In my expert opinion, I would say the going-home club is the absolute best.
You are just goofing off during the period you can goof off the most,
and that makes you a winner in my book.
Keep on lazing around and make money from me.
I get treated like a weirdo just for being in this club!
A club must have five or more members, right?
We have to find new members like our lives depend on it!
That is got to be it!
I just received a submission of resignation from this club, so be forewarned...
This club will now be abolished.
Sadly, I am going to have to ask you to gather all of your things.
I actually just had a brand-new club request a club room.
I am not going to let you abolish the Telepathy Club!
The Telepathy Club bond is strong.
The student council's got nothing on us!
You think you are all high-and-mighty because of how you part your hair?!
Do you really want me to get angry?
If you are that desperate to keep this club going,
bring me a new club member by the end of the school day on Friday.
That only gives us two days.
If we ask everyone we see to join, we will be able to snag at least one!
Recruiting season ended a long time ago.
I am going to do this!
We have overcome so many obstacles up until now, have not we?!
We have not done a single thing...
Sorry, what the hell are you talking about?
We have got entrance exams this year.
Do you have any hot guys?
I want to be able to date.
I would be worried about the stares, and it seems dangerous.
It really was impossible to find new members this time of the year.
Not to mention we just keep getting called creepy.
Now even I want to quit.
He is not in any clubs or committees,
and he does not seem to have a girlfriend or any friends.
Salt Middle School's final go-homer and all-round bum,
Let me introduce you to the other members, Kageyama-kun.
And I am the president, Kurata Tome, from class 3-5.
I-I am sure that is because of fate, too!
After this, I have to go to my exorcism job.
What is that supposed to mean?
Actually, this guy was sort of famous in grade school.
He could bend spoons and make erasers move...
Stop being weird and just join our club.
I am sure the exorcism can wait a little while.
Is it all right if I am a little late today?
I am being recruited into a club.
No, I actually have to wait until the student council meeting is over,
and then go submit my club admission form.
So if I tell you I need you to come immediately, you are not going to join?
Should not I keep the promise I made first?
So it is not like you actually want to join?
Show them how fast someone in the going-home club can leave school.
He says he needs me right away, so I will be going now.
P-Put me on for a sec!
I really need Kageyama-kun to join this club, no matter what!
She must be trying to use Mob.
Mob's not the type to play any sports.
Forcing him into things is not good.
We are not a sports club!
It is a club where we train in order to feel telepathic powers.
Yeah, that sounds shady as hell.
Like you are one to talk!
I heard that Kageyama-kun has ESP,
but are not you using that to get more customers?
Do not you dare try to steal away my student's precious time with your nonsense!
Are you saying that you do not care if our club gets abolished?
We are going to be kicked out of the room!
Master, Senpai is about to cry, so I am thinking about joining after all...
Like any of those things will disappear because a club is abolished.
They just do not want to lose their room, their budget
and their pointless after-school time, judging from what their club sounds like.
That shady club is going down because it is meant to go down.
If you understand, hurry up and come to work!
And so, I will be leaving after all.
It seems that the president seriously believes in telepathy,
but honestly, yeah, I just want to goof off.
But right now, we are in middle school.
This is the only time we are going to be able to goof off!
Play cards with us in this lazy little paradise we have created!
You are not going to find a more carefree club than this.
We have until tomorrow, so think it over.
You are our last hope, Kageyama-kun!
You properly declined, did not you?
I thought I would think about it overnight.
You need to properly decline things that you do not want to do.
Right now, the thing I least want to do
It is a private all-girls high school.
We are meeting the clients up on the roof.
Hey, that is a bit mean, is not it?
I knew this would not work.
But thank goodness that they saw through our disguises so early.
I did not want to infiltrate the school dressed up like this.
Now hurry up and get away from the pervert.
We will deal with the suspicious individual.
Will not I get in a lot of trouble if I am busted?
He said we were meeting on the roof, but...
I have come from the consultation office.
You trying to get through to us thugs?
Like we are going to let some twerp like you lecture us!
Why do not you mind your own business?!
If you do not, you are going to regret it!
You promptly got picked on by thugs.
Is not that Reigen guy coming?
He was caught at the front gate.
Also, you both came here dressed as girls?
He could not get us permission to come in, so we did not have a choice...
Sorry to make you go through all that.
The school just refuses to take us seriously.
Students' belongings have been disappearing under mysterious circumstances,
and we have been hearing weird noises...
What do you call it, a poltergeist phenomenon?
We heard things have been spotted floating through the air, too.
Apparently a bra started floating around on its own in the locker room.
We are dead sure it has to be something supernatural.
So we just called the cheapest exorcist in the area
and somehow ended up with you.
You are a guy, but you were trembling so much dealing with some high school girls.
You must be quite the reliable gentleman.
Are you sure we can trust you?
I just have to perform an exorcism.
If you feel anything spiritual, let us know.
I wonder if he is being serious...
Something was looking in from the top of the door...
And no one's gone through the exit.
I am going to follow the spirit.
If we keep pursuing it, it might try to do something.
What are we going to do?
The basketball team is practicing inside.
I am going to end this.
Are you going to try to ruin my paradise?
If I do not take a hostage, he will erase me!
Want to go home together today?
Apparently you were pretty reliable after all.
To think that I was defeated by a loser like you...
And I thought I would finally be able to be happy.
You seem to be similar to me.
The way you get nervous around girls...
You are playing the loser role in youth just like me, are not you?
Things finally started to get fun for me after I died.
But I guess it is all over now.
Are you living every day to the fullest?
Now, hurry up and sign this club admission form.
Well, I had to show this room...
This room will become the club room
for the newly formed Body Improvement Club.
The Telepathy Club will not be abolished!
Kageyama-kun here is just about to join!
Do you have any experience in other clubs?
Do you have a close friend in the Telepathy Club?
Do you go to cram school?
Do not you have anything that you want to do?
If you let them goad you into joining despite having no interest in the club at all,
what exactly will you gain from it?
Well, I just want to live every day to the fullest.
And will spending your time after school with cola, snacks and video games
If you want to join of your own free will, I will not stop you.
However, you should carefully reconsider this.
What is it that you really want to do?
Do I have anything I want to do?
Hanging out with girls might be fun...
I wanted to confess my feelings to my first love, Tsubomi-chan,
and walk home together, holding hands.
When you make frogs float, they start swimming.
I can make the bar all squishy.
I am only showing you, Tsubomi-chan!
If I can change anything by joining a club...
I will join the Body Improvement Club.
